      "level": "medium",
      "rationale": "Two independent metrics (rule-based + LLM-judge); apples-to-apples comparison across two agent versions via the same persona prompts; deterministic + LLM-judge mix. Weaknesses: small corpus, no human-judge alignment study, single-judge ensemble."
